{
  "stem": "4967.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I can't remember at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I think it was coupons we could buy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Yes, we used to buy actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We used to be paid with German currency at work, and then we used to buy food, which is-- it's laughable, especially in winter.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We used to get frozen potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We used to see the potato.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "When you come home, you see mash.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You couldn't even cook it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then after a day or two, they start to smell, excuse me, terrible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we used to buy by the coupons bread, flour and other stuff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The main survival in the ghetto was to organize how to sell your belongings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "You used to trade in over the fence with the Lithuanians your clothing, your-- if somebody had some money, or diamonds, or goods, outfits, bed sheets, over the wall, over-- not far from the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the [NON-ENGLISH], the non-Jewish, they used to give you meat, fruit, flour, potatoes, whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the ghetto, from time to time, became smaller.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Oh, by the way, they builded another ghetto on the other side of the road, which are-- because some people came from some other places, and the ghetto was too small.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they built a bridge between the two ghettos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And at the bottom of the bridge was the main road, which is going to [NON-ENGLISH] Kovno, and to the outskirts somewhere.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And in, in the main ghetto was also a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But the Germans-- excuse me-- the Germans didn't show any films there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They put accommodation for people who used to come in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They used to sleep on the floor, people come from villages, Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they used to stay there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And the people used to carry on working there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
